Apologies about that... I did my final test on Windows with a different version as I released on accident. The newest version is now up on PyPI and should fix any issues.

Upgrade with 
```
pip install stata_kernel --upgrade
```

and
```
pip show stata_kernel
```
should show version 1.10.1
